  - id: card_0014_desc
    textList:
    - language: 0
      text: Lose 10% Max HP. Gain 1 Berserk & 80 Stamina.
    - language: 1
      text: "M\u1EA5t 10% L\u01B0\u1EE3ng M\xE1u T\u1ED1i \u0110a. Nh\u1EADn 1 hi\u1EC7u
